def_cn: 室女宫，室女座（黄道十二宫之一。出生于8月23日至9月22日之间的人属此星座）
def_en: Virgo is one of the twelve signs of the zodiac. Its symbol is a young woman. People who are born approximately between the 23rd of August and the 22nd of September come under this sign.

def_cn: 出生于室女宫时段的人
def_en: A Virgo is a person whose sign of the zodiac is Virgo.
